S.FORM: aicu ti Kuo Hsing-Chun (ciniukukan:郭婞淳；inamizukuan:Tana) mavan a unduin nase 舉重 nua aya. nalemedaw kemasi imaza i yilan king. timadju kemasi imaza i taitu i valangaw a qinaljan uta. na kitjuala kemasi i na pakata undu kaucung a gaku kitjeljc sihu taitu daigaku katua nase tinsiukiu kuzing a vuren daigaku itua undu a tatuluan . avan sika tucu namasan tua huciawsu imaza i vuren daigaku se undu a tatuluan. timadju namalap tua liawliaw a pazangal a tjaljavavavan a pakaleva nase paqaqayam a 舉重, parutua ka 2020 a caviljan aulingpiya undukai imaza i ripun i tukiyu, na kialap tua sangasangasan a pakaleva pakata 舉重 nase vavayan a 59 a kinasadjelung katua mareka paqaqayam imaza i kacauan. ka 2017 a caviljan timajdu na paselaw tjaljavavavan a tinsu izua 142 a kinasadjelung itua 挺舉, namsan ta sangasangasan a tinsu se vavayan a unduin i kacauan tuazua. ka tjaivililj ta 2018 a caviljan patje tucu timadju mavananga tjaljasangasangasan a unduin nasevavayan namalap tua vavavan a tinsu pakata 59 a kinasadjelung itua 抓舉, 挺舉, katua penuljat a tinsu matja tjelu a 項目 i kacauan. kipalikuzan == pakaleva ==

aico ti Koo Hsing-Chon (ciniokokan:郭婞淳；inamizokoan:Tana) mavan a ondoin nase 舉重 noa aya. nalemedaw kemasi imaza i yilan king. timadjo kemasi imaza i taito i valangaw a qinaljan ota. na kitjoala kemasi i na pakata ondo kaocong a gako kitjeljc siho taito daigako katoa nase tinsiokio kozing a voren daigako itoa ondo a tatoloan . avan sika toco namasan toa hociawso imaza i voren daigako se ondo a tatoloan. timadjo namalap toa liawliaw a pazangal a tjaljavavavan a pakaleva nase paqaqayam a 舉重, parotoa ka 2020 a caviljan aolingpiya ondokai imaza i ripon i tokiyo, na kialap toa sangasangasan a pakaleva pakata 舉重 nase vavayan a 59 a kinasadjelong katoa mareka paqaqayam imaza i kacaoan. ka 2017 a caviljan timajdo na paselaw tjaljavavavan a tinso izoa 142 a kinasadjelong itoa 挺舉, namsan ta sangasangasan a tinso se vavayan a ondoin i kacaoan toazoa. ka tjaivililj ta 2018 a caviljan patje toco timadjo mavananga tjaljasangasangasan a ondoin nasevavayan namalap toa vavavan a tinso pakata 59 a kinasadjelong itoa 抓舉, 挺舉, katoa penoljat a tinso matja tjelo a 項目 i kacaoan. kipalikozan == pakaleva ==
